observationText: The PlpCreERT; Nf1flox/flox; eGFP mouse model was generated by breeding a b-actin flox/stop/flox-EGFP mouse reporter line onto the Nf1flox/flox background.

In the PlpCreERT; Nf1flox/flox; eGFP mouse model, EGFP-positive cells were present in the dorsal and ventral root boundary cap zones and proximal peripheral nerve at embryonic day 12.5, but not within the dorsal root ganglion.
In adult PlpCreERT; Nf1flox/flox; eGFP mice, EGFP-positive cells were present in the dorsal root ganglion, peripheral nerve, and nerve roots.
